descp2: array-like of shape (n_classes,) or (n_classes - 1,),              (default=None) The proportions of samples assigned to each class. If None, then classes are balanced. Note that if ``len(weights) == n_classes - 1``, then the last class weight is automatically inferred. More than ``n_samples`` samples may be returned if the sum of ``weights`` exceeds 1.
